text:
{
  "prompt": "A quiet coastal seafood restaurant at night named 'Eochon Hoetjip', located in an urban area. The surrounding city is dark and peaceful, with subtle streetlights, a hint of neon signs in the distance, and the restaurant glowing warmly with indoor light. The scene has a cinematic, almost poetic mood, capturing the contrast between the dark city and the cozy, inviting seafood restaurant.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A night scene of a quiet Korean coastal town. The atmosphere is serene and a bit mysterious, with dim lighting from nearby seafood restaurants, including one called '어촌 횟집'. In the foreground, a man who appears to be in his early 30s stands confidently. He has a youthful appearance, short black hair, clear skin, and is dressed casually but neatly. The overall mood is introspective and calm, with a soft sea breeze and faint city lights in the distance.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic photo of a middle-aged East Asian man sitting on a chair in Seongsu-dong, Seoul, enjoying a fresh plate of assorted sashimi (including sea cucumber) as if he were by the sea. The atmosphere feels like a quiet coastal town, even though it is in the city. The man is relaxed, leaning back slightly, with a peaceful expression. The setting includes urban buildings in the background but has a serene, seaside-style dining mood.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A realistic 3D rendering of a full suspension electric bicycle designed for a 180cm tall rider. The bike has 20-inch (406) wheels with 3-inch wide on-road tires. The frame is optimized for central mid-drive motor (48V 500W) and features a full air suspension system (front and rear). The design includes a step-through frame for ease of mounting, hydraulic disc brakes, and a low-mounted battery along the down tube. The color scheme is metallic dark grey with subtle blue accents. The rear suspension is mounted horizontally with a visible air shock absorber. The front suspension fork is thick and robust, supporting wide tires. Urban background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered digital image of a 20-inch full-suspension electric bicycle with a step-through frame and a rear cargo rack. The bike features a mid-drive 48V 500W motor, front and rear air suspension, 3-inch wide on-road tires on 406 wheels, and a clean, urban-ready design. The frame is designed for comfort and utility, suitable for delivery or commuting use.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A 3D-rendered electric bicycle with a top-down integrated downtube design, step-through frame, and rear cargo rack. The tires are 20-inch, 3-inch wide on-road style, designed for city commuting. The frame is sleek and modern with full air suspension both front and rear. The battery is housed inside the downtube.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A futuristic, step-through electric bicycle with a belt drive system and an internal-gear hub. The design features no top tube (open frame geometry), a sleek swingarm-style rear suspension with high responsiveness, and a 3-inch wide on-road tire. The frame is minimalist and modern, optimized for urban delivery, with a cargo rack integrated at the rear. The background is clean and minimal to emphasize the bicycle's design.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A high-resolution digital render of a modern electric bicycle with a belt drive and internal gear hub. The frame is painted red, featuring a step-through design with the top tube removed. The battery is integrated into the upper part of the downtube. The rear swingarm suspension is active and articulated. The bike is equipped with 20-inch wheels and 3-inch wide on-road tires. The design emphasizes urban utility and modern aesthetics.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A diagram showing different types of bicycle and motorcycle full suspension frame designs, each labeled and visually distinct. The bicycle section includes Single Pivot, Horst Link, Four-Bar Linkage, VPP (Virtual Pivot Point), DW-Link, and Soft Tail. The motorcycle section includes Double Cradle with Swingarm, Monocoque with Hydraulic Link, Cast Aluminum Frame, Dual Link Swingarm, and Parallelogram Suspension. Each design is shown with a simplified technical drawing in side profile, highlighting pivot points and suspension elements. Clean, educational style illustration.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
